## **Common Corp/State Tricks — And How You Crush Them**

| **Their Lie** | **Your Counter** |
|-------------|-----------------|
| “You relinquished—lost rights” | **LIE** — §7(o) is **ANCSA**, not tribal. 2016 case proves it. |
| “All heirs as one” | **LIE** — §7(o) is **individual**. Notti v. CIRI. |
| “7(i) debt forces sale” | **LIE** — §7(o) trumps debt. 2018 Doyon case. |
| “Court approved it” | **LIE** — Federal law > state court. File in U.S. District. |

